---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";
import Header from "../components/layout/Header.astro";
import Footer from "../components/layout/Footer.astro";
---

<Layout>
	<Header />
	<main class="py-16 lg:py-24 bg-white">
		<div class="px-6 md:px-10 lg:px-16 max-w-3xl mx-auto">
			<h1 class="text-heading-section text-kfood-primary mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>
			<p class="font-body text-kfood-body text-lg leading-relaxed mb-10">
				At KFood, we are committed to protecting your personal data and your right to privacy. This Privacy Policy governs the privacy terms of our website and explains how we collect, protect, and use your information.
			</p>

			<div class="legal-content space-y-8 font-body text-kfood-body">
				<section>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold text-kfood-primary mb-3">1. Information We Collect</h2>
					<p class="leading-relaxed mb-3">
						We collect personal information that you voluntarily provide to us when registering on the website, placing an order, or contacting us. This includes:
					</p>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
						<li><strong>Personal Identifiers:</strong> Name, shipping address, and billing address.</li>
						<li><strong>Contact Information:</strong> Email address and phone number.</li>
						<li><strong>Payment Data:</strong> Necessary information to process your payment (processed via secure third-party gateways).</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold text-kfood-primary mb-3">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
					<p class="leading-relaxed mb-3">
						We use the information we collect solely for professional purposes, including:
					</p>
					<ul class="list-disc pl-6 space-y-1">
						<li>To fulfill and manage your orders and deliveries.</li>
						<li>To communicate with you regarding account updates or promotional offers.</li>
						<li>To improve our website functionality and customer service.</li>
					</ul>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold text-kfood-primary mb-3">3. Data Sharing and Disclosure</h2>
					<p class="leading-relaxed">
						KFood does not sell, rent, or trade your personal information to third parties. We only share information with third-party service providers (such as courier services) to the extent necessary to complete your transactions.
					</p>
				</section>

				<section>
					<h2 class="text-xl font-heading font-semibold text-kfood-primary mb-3">4. Data Security</h2>
					<p class="leading-relaxed">
						We implement industry-standard security measures to maintain the safety of your personal information. However, please note that no method of transmission over the internet is 100% secure.
					</p>
				</section>
			</div>

			<p class="mt-12 font-body text-muted text-sm">
				Last updated: February 2025. For questions, contact us at <a href="mailto:contact@kfood.pk" class="text-kfood-primary underline">contact@kfood.pk</a>.
			</p>
		</div>
	</main>
	<Footer />
</Layout>
